Show HN: 13Sheep – a JavaScript game largely authored by ChatGPT
text: 13 Sheep is a quick roll-and-write game for one or more players. By drawing fences on a grid, players try to protect as many sheep as possible before the wolf comes. I reproduced the rules in an online experience, allowing for additional user customization compared to the pen and paper version. A lot of the code comes from a conversation I had with chatGPT.
